NSLOCTEXT("", "20A174E34BD06EC5A66107A41DAA3D86", "The Lumberjack operates from this house, to cut down trees in the area you specified.

Produces Logs.

A lumberjack needs to work in the woodcutters'.")

NSLOCTEXT("", "7F7B34614A0D497383C3F1ADB5E2C4EB", "In the sawmill, the carpenter saws logs into useable wooden planks.

Requires Logs.
Produces Lumber

A carpenter needs to work in the sawmill.")

NSLOCTEXT("", "A70E550E4AB6F00675E49196DC8543F1", "The bakery houses a large furnace in which the baker bakes his delicious bread.

Requires Flour.
Produces Bread.

A baker needs to work in the bakery.")
